scripts.testallversions: npm run node010 && npm run node4 && npm run node6 && npm run node9 && npm run node11
scripts.testversion: docker run -it --rm -v $(PWD):/usr/src/app -w /usr/src/app node:${NODE_VER} npm install mocha@${MOCHA_VER:-latest} && npm t
scripts.postpublish: git push origin && git push origin --tags
